descriptionHtml:

[color=#b6d7a8]Credit to [color=#d5a6bd][b]Jokerine[/b][/color] for the Forever Free! logo, download from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/58832/?]here.[/url][/color][/size][color=#b6d7a8][size=3]

[size=5]Riften PLayer's Warehouse.[/size]
[color=#ffe599]+ Russian Translation ( 3 in 1 ) - Русский перевод[/color]
Credit and Thank You to Sergoramus :-)

This is a home for the Player to stack his/her loot. There is also a pool and a basement that is equipped with a dining table and chairs and 2 beds and a Talos Shrine so you can clean yourself after whatever you do in Skyrim.

There are 3 choises:
-Riften Player's Warehouse (with female NPCs)
-Riften Player's Warehouse No NPC
-Riften Player's Warehouse Male NPC

If you want the tropical looks you need to install [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33017/?]Soolie's Tropical Skyrim[/url]. It is a total overhaul bringing tropical climate, vegetations and animals to Skyrim - Remember to credit Soolie and donate if that suits you.

I have created a plugin replacer - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/74308/]Tropical Skyrim II[/url] - that cleans up paths in caves and dungeons.

Credit to:
-Tamira for Skyrim version of "New Plants" [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22018/?]here[/url].
-Tiwa44 for UNP Minidresses Collection [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/47376/?]here[/url].
-Brokefoot for UNP Mashup Compilation [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/20415/?]here[/url].

This mod also works [u]without[/u] Tropical Skyrim.

Thanks to Bethesda Softworks for creating wonderous games.
Thanks to my friends on the nexusmods.[/size][/color]
